However, hand washing promotion significantly reduces diarrhoeal diseases. In support of Handwashing Day, marked on October 15, South Africa has dedicated the month of October to National Handwashing Month. 

In partnership with the country's Department of Education, the hygiene brand Dettol is teaching young people about personal hygiene nationally. 

Doctor Sindi van Zyl, is a general practitioner in the country supporting Dettol's initiative… --ChannelAfrica--